{"tid":832273,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"[又係我呀]Umarex P-08 WWII edition","createTime":"2018-09-22T15:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T08:19:41.000Z","uid":143499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"afa34cc9ba3a919b5ebb2f4620f59fb90ffb4058","tid":832273,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T15:56:19.000Z","msg":"小弟今日用六嚿幾水買咗把嘢，支嘢用co2， 而彈藥就係4.5 mm steel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官方fps係300，而每粒4.5 mm steel BB 重0.32至0.34 gram<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n計番起啫係每槍1.3至1.4焦耳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想問殺傷力會唔會太大？<br />\n<br />\n以前玩開green gas氣槍都係0.9幾焦耳， 今日燒槍嗰陣打到鋁板穿窿咁濟，搞到而家唔敢再用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實1.4焦耳係咪好容易入肉，雖則香港法例係低於兩焦耳( 利申淨係諗住射死物 ) 但係好驚整到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98320ea1e906521120abf071da2b695f833b4d55","tid":832273,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:10:44.000Z","msg":"今晚up唔到圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4246d91f3ce853101d946da5bd158e83869cca5","tid":832273,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T03:01:15.000Z","msg":"屋企玩1.4焦耳嘅槍會唔會太危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ddc2fe4f4af66cad3795f56b28c0043601ec26","tid":832273,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T07:58:12.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d6b709ec569a1f798982481a9da86be149ed675","tid":832273,"uid":60287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T07:32:11.000Z","msg":"4.5mm鋼珠唔係用黎俾你射人打game㗎哥仔"},{"pid":"cc6307659b965015b22d1b17c9ace09c4154a913","tid":832273,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d6b709ec569a1f79